    "This integration offers several advantages; it improves item similarity by incorporating ontology-based semantic knowledge alongside item ratings.",
    "It also addresses common issues in collaborative filtering, such as sparsity and cold-start items.",
    "Ultimately, this approach holds the promise of significantly boosting prediction accuracy in recommendations.The framework of the proposed semantic-based improved collaborative filtering approach is presented in Fig. 2.",
    "It consists of four main phases.",
    "The first phase constructs the ontology repository of the considered domain."
